Source URL:
- https://github.com/motdotla/dotenv
Fetched: 2026-02-27

dotenv usage notes:
- Load as early as possible in process startup.
- config() defaults to .env in current working directory.
- path option supports custom env path.
- CLI preload supported via node -r dotenv/config.

Implementation implications:
- Keep config() at top-level bootstrap for API provider modules.
- Avoid late env-loading after provider singleton initialization.
